file.name: OneOf.v1.yml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  title: OneOf.v1
  version: '1.0'
servers:
  - url: 'http://localhost:3000'
paths:
  /pets:
    patch:
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              oneOf:
                - $ref: '#/components/schemas/Cat'
                - $ref: '#/components/schemas/Dog'
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Updated
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                oneOf:
                  - $ref: '#/components/schemas/Cat'
                  - $ref: '#/components/schemas/Dog'
components:
  schemas:
    Dog:
      type: object
      properties:
        bark:
          type: boolean
        breed:
          type: string
          enum: [Dingo, Husky, Retriever, Shepherd]
      additionalProperties: false
    Cat:
      type: object
      properties:
        hunts:
          type: boolean
        age:
          type: integer
      additionalProperties: false
